\
## Hallucination Reduction Strategy\
\
Implement all of the following:\
\
1. retrieval-gated answering\
2. citation-required response formatting\
3. confidence scoring\
4. "insufficient evidence" response path\
5. conflict detection across sources\
6. exact page preview link in UI\
7. source snippet display beside every answer\
8. aircraft-level and tenant-level filters on retrieval\
9. separate extracted metadata from inferred metadata\
10. full audit logging\
\
