## Permissions and Roles\
\
Roles:\
- Owner / Admin\
- Mechanic / Editor\
- Viewer\
- External Auditor / Inspector (view-only, optional)\
- Broker / Buyer (temporary data room access, later)\
\
Rules:\
- all retrieval queries must be scoped by organization\
- all document fetches must respect row-level security\
- users only see aircraft and documents they have access to\
