## Google Drive Integration\
\
Requirements:\
- OAuth sign-in to Google\
- picker for file/folder selection\
- ingest PDF files\
- retain Drive file ID and source URL\
- allow manual re-sync\
- avoid deleting original source file\
- store imported copy in Supabase Storage for stable processing\
