\
## OCR and Document Handling\
\
Support these lanes:\
\
### Lane A \'97 clean digital PDFs\
- full automation\
- highest confidence\
\
### Lane B \'97 scanned PDFs\
- OCR\
- confidence scoring\
- page previews\
\
### Lane C \'97 handwritten logbooks\
- advanced OCR pipeline\
- lower confidence allowed\
- optional human verification workflow for critical pages\
\
Do not claim perfect handwritten extraction.\
